divs: sighting detailsi was watching the vikings \ packers game, my wife went outside to smoke and called me out to show me something "you have to see this". starting due west over the white tank mountains, 3 redish \ orange pusalting orbs in unchanging triangular formation moved to the n-nw for about a minute and a half then moved closer together then one by one disappeared up and to back to the west.
